overview:
Peter has extensive on-demand technology sales experience. Most recently he served as vice president of sales for Angel Points Inc., an innovative workforce management application for Fortune 100 companies. Peter spent over five years at Salesforce.com. He was a founding member of the sales organization and the first account executive for Strategic Accounts in the Enterprise Group. At Paychex Corporation, an HR and payroll process software company, Peter served as sales representative for major markets. Peter graduated from Ohio University.

Source : Marinsoftware.com
